        <odd id="ref11">
            <head>Early American History Note</head>
            <p>This collection contains meteorological observations compiled by John Heckewelder in Pennsylvania and George Miller in Ohio for the years 1800-1812. The observations are sporadic. They are especially detailed for 1800-1802 and 1810-1812.</p>
